subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. ORIENTAL: China (* Fujian , * Guangdong , * Guangxi , Jiangxi , * Taiwan) . PALAEARCTIC: China ( Gansu , Liaoning ) (
Chen et al. 2019
).
